sources.title: Dark Island | Full Movie | Action Sci-Fi Horror | Killer Virus!
sources.description:
Dark Island - After losing contact with its researchers on a remote island, a military corporation hires a group of scientists and soldiers to find out what went wrong. When they arrive, the team quickly discovers that experiments performed on the island have unleashed a powerful and deadly entity that will stop at nothing to destroy them all.
2010.  Stars: Jai Koutrae, Mary Christina Brown, Tate Ammons, Tess Panzer, Brandon Laatsch
